vote.title: An ordinance abandoning all of two water easements and a portion of a drainage easement to Victory Block M LP, the abutting owner, containing a total of approximately 4,242 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Museum Way and Victory Avenue; and providing for the dedication of approximately 4,288 square feet of land needed for a drainage easement - Revenue: General Fund $7,800.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
